item.title: Recloud Challenge 2021
item.description: Recloud Challenges 2021, Come on, Join Next Season In 2021, an event has been held for programmers, especially web programmers for the most beautiful and good website possible because there is a prize with a large nominal for the winner of the event. At the event I participated and got a certificate. And yeah that was my experience joining the biggest web programming event in Indonesia.
